         <Common_Consequences>
            <Consequence>
               <Scope>Access Control</Scope>
               <Scope>Other</Scope>
               <Impact>Bypass Protection Mechanism</Impact>
               <Impact>Other</Impact>
               <Note>When authorization, authentication, or another protection mechanism relies on CAPTCHA entities to ensure that only human actors can access certain functionality, then an automated attacker such as a bot may access the restricted functionality by guessing the CAPTCHA.</Note>
            </Consequence>
         </Common_Consequences>
